    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk, the help stuff just feels so performative u know? like it's just words. the reality is i'm just a blip. i look at people walking by and i realize i don't leave a footprint. if i just... faded away, there wouldn't even be a mess to clean up. it almost sounds peaceful, thinking about just not having to carry the weight of being seen anymore.",
